sequenceDiagram
    actor Analyst as 👤 Analyst
    participant Excel as 📊 Excel Reviews
    participant System as 🤖 AI Tool
    participant PE as ⚙️ Prompt Engineering
    participant LLM as 🧠 LLM
    participant Report as 📄 Report
    
    Analyst->>Excel: Complete review work<br/>(Findings, Recommendations, Frameworks)
    Analyst->>System: Upload Excel file
    
    System->>Excel: Extract content & context
    Excel-->>System: Return structured data
    
    System->>PE: Send extracted data
    PE->>PE: Build prompts with:<br/>• Context from Excel<br/>• Structure templates<br/>• Linking instructions
    PE-->>System: Optimized prompt ready
    
    System->>LLM: Send prompt + context
    LLM->>LLM: Process & generate:<br/>• Connect findings<br/>• Link recommendations<br/>• Create narrative<br/>• Format report
    LLM-->>System: Generated report content
    
    System->>Report: Compile final document
    Report-->>Analyst: ✅ Ready-to-use report
    
    Note over Analyst,Report: ⚡ Automated process eliminates manual rewriting
